message: First pass at vertical timeline view re #3
Uses normalizePath from Obsidian API re #22
Fix PR/merge bugs for start and end time
Add start hour, clean up logic
Add stylelint with some sensible defaults

Rewrite parser

* The previous parser needlessly hoarded state. The new one is a pure
  function
refactor: add eslint-import and apply fixes
build: add formatting script; add stylelint to linting
feat: add arrows to header; fix lucide-svelte
build: add support for @testing-library/svelte; comment out broken tests
feat: add 'go to previous week' button

feat: 'colorful' timeline

adds back an optional gradient to the timeline.
feat: display sub-items in task blocks
fix: display copied task in correct place at once
refactor: add more tests; split code again
feat: improve remote task visuals, add settings
refactor: use more generic pointer events
refactor: remove imperative floating ui logic
chore: use strict TS in development workflow
chore: use strict TS in plan ts files
fix: fix type errors in Svelte files
chore: raise deps to latest versions

fix: fix dependency errors

* Pin 'moment' to the same version that Obsidian
  exports to fix TypeScript grief.
* Ignore peer dependency errors from
  overlay-scrollbars, which work with Svelte 5
  anyway.
fix: fix plugin not loading on mobile
fix: revert ical to prevent bugs until forced to update
